data.description: Step into this exquisite custom-decorated tri-level home boasting elegance and comfort at every turn. With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this immaculate residence offers the perfect blend of sophistication and functionality. The lower level surprises with a delightful bonus Jacuzzi room, perfect for relaxation. The room could be updated to a home office or media room. Experience the epitome of luxury with ceramic tile and hardwood floors throughout, enhancing the charm of each room. Entertain effortlessly with a custom deck accessible from the dining room, ideal for hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings under the stars.    Meticulously maintained this home radiates pride of ownership and is ready for immediate occupancy. Move right in and start creating unforgettable memories in this absolutely beautiful space.    Don't miss out on this rare opportunity! Schedule your viewing today and see for yourself the unparalleled beauty and elegance of this home. 24-hour notice required for showings.
